skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: red flag dealbreaker full send
des: Red Flag, DealBreaker, Full Send offers prompts that describe potentially controversial traits in the people you date (or choose not to date). Alexa shares a prompt, which you can mull over, come to a final response (red flag, dealbreaker, or full send), and ask for the next prompt. There are no right answers - everyone draws their own line!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
